msgid "bug-of-the-month club"
msgstr "bug-of-the-month club"

#: ../../B/bug-of-the-month-club.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../B/bug-of-the-month-club.rst:9
msgid ""
"[from \"book-of-the-month club\", a time-honored mail-order-marketing "
"technique in the U.S.] A mythical club which users of :manpage:`sendmail(8)`"
" (the Unix mail daemon) belong to; this was coined on the Usenet newsgroup "
"comp.security.unix at a time when sendmail security holes, which allowed "
"outside :ref:`cracker`\\s access to the system, were being uncovered at an "
"alarming rate, forcing sysadmins to update very often. Also, more "
"completely, fatal security bug-of-the-month club. See also :ref:`kernel-of-"
"the-week-club`\\."
msgstr ""
"[米国で由緒ある通信販売マーケティング手法「book-of-the-month club(月刊書籍クラブ)」から]\\ "
":manpage:`sendmail(8)`\\ (Unixのメールデーモン)のユーザーが所属する架空のクラブ。外部の\\ "
":ref:`cracker`\\ "
"にシステムへのアクセスを許すsendmailのセキュリティホールが憂慮すべき速さで次々に発見され、システム管理者が非常に頻繁に更新を強いられていた時期に、Usenetのニュースグループcomp.security.unixで造られた。より完全には、fatal"
" security bug-of-the-month club(致命的セキュリティバグ月刊クラブ)とも。\\ :ref:`kernel-of-the-"
"week-club`\\ も参照。"
